    "Name": "Bombardier",
    "Details": "This, arguably, Sidegrade of a Bombardier still does the Job it was supposed to do. Now armed with 4 MML's instead of a mix of SRM's and LRM launchers, it still gets the Support Role done. You can see a whole Plethora of ideas were included into this Refit, but im not too sure how its going to work out. According to all Sources i can find, This was built somewhere in the FWL just before they Fragmented, so they probably slapped on whatever they had and went to War with it. The name doesnt Ring a bell though, i have to wonder what it means.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>",
