  "StockRole": "Heavy Support",
  "YangsThoughts": "4 MML Launchers and a Light AC5 in the Centertorso is the Mainstay Weapon of this Mech. It has a Narc Launcher for giving others a Helping Hand, but other than that it does its own Job. Whats more surprising to me is the Reactive Armour and the Endo Composite, both Very Rare and Hard to Install. Theres also a Shield in the Left side, giving it some more Protection from incoming Fire. A Skilled Mechwarrior can do some Real damage with this, if he uses the shield to his Advantage. Sadly theres no Case in this, so if you get hit in the Ammo, the whole Mech is going to Blast off into Space.",
